ore":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T12:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雖然我咁講姐 不過我自己呢<br />\n就要求好高<br />\n唔係強烈有feel都唔會一齊<br />\n<br />\n女仔拍拖謹慎啲既<br />\n你男人就是但啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同巴打諗嘅差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好難先會好強烈咁鍾意一個人<br />\n因為我以前追過個女仔 但喺畀佢拒絕咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我成日會諗而家呢個人冇以前我追嗰個咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以對佢唔會有好強烈嘅feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我對住鍾意既人會忍佢忍得好勁<br />\n點嘈交都唔會走<br />\n就算佢發脾氣個樣 都覺得好順眼<br />\n<br />\n相反，對住唔係太有feel果個<br />\n見到佢發嬲<br />\n會諗乜撚野事，覺得好樣衰唔想忍（但其實佢樣ok）"},{"pid":"f729d83e3d19bbe350bce5ac3f12b2132966559e","tid":506641,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T12:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>利申非FF <br />\n唔好同我講嗰啲死毒撚唔好FF咁多之類嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前排有個女仔同我告白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話鍾意咗我好耐 但喺一直唔敢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我對佢其實唔係話完全冇Feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都算喺有少少好感 但喺又未到話鍾意到一定要一齊嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢幾靚女 但係真喺未到嗰種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我怕接受咗就好似呃緊佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但喺拒絕嘅話又怕自己將來會後悔 會錯過咗一個愛我嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你喺我 你會唔會接受佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會 感情可以慢慢培養<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會 唔好呃人感情啦</blockquote><br />\n我對佢其實唔係話完全冇Feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.g